<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../shared/css/content.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../shared/css/module1.css" />
    <script src="../shared/js/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../shared/js/jquery/jquery.transit.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../shared/js/jquery/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../shared/css/module1_2.css" />
    <style> 
        .resultdiv .rbox .btns A{color:#fff;background:none;}
        .resultdiv .rbox .btns A:hover{color:#000000;}
        .resultdiv .rbox STRONG {  font-family: Avenir Next LT Pro Regular; font-weight:900; }
        .fontpreloader { position:absolute; left:-100px; top:-100px; width:1px; height:1px; font-size:1px; font-family: Avenir Next LT Pro Regular; }
        .fontpreloader1 { position:absolute; left:-100px; top:-100px; width:1px; height:1px; font-size:1px; font-family: SEGOEUIL; }
        .visited{};
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="content">
    	<div class="fontpreloader">.</div>
    	<div class="fontpreloader1">.</div>
    	<img src="images/canvas-clouds.jpg" style="height:0px; width:0px; float:left; opacity: 0">
        <div class="rbox" style="height:0px; width:0px;"></div>
         
        <div class="resultbg"></div>
        <div id="idiv" class="resultdiv">
            <div class="rbox">
                <p style="font-size:11pt">Why are interviews conducted in the first place? You know the answer to this already. However, the purpose of the mock interview is to ensure that candidates appearing for the interview are also aware why interviews are conducted.</p>
                <p style="font-size:11pt">Share this knowledge with candidates during the mock interview to enable them to be better prepared for the actual interview. Let’s play a game to refresh your memory. </p>
                <p style="font-size:11pt">A few balloons are floating, each of which has one reason why you need to conduct an interview. Pick the right reasons by clicking on the floating balloon. </p>
                <p style=" font-size: 11pt;">You have 30 seconds to finish this game. Click <strong>Start</strong> to begin. </p>
                <div class="btns" style="margin-top:20px;"><a class="btn" id="btn_start" style="background-image: url('images/cnt_btn_new.png');width: 91px;height: 30px;background-repeat: no-repeat;margin: 0px -15px;">Start</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="rdiv" class="resultdiv">
            <div class="rbox">
                <h3></h3>
                <div class="correct">
                    <p>Well done! You have identified all the reasons for conducting the interview correctly. </p>
                    <p>You can click <strong>Play Again</strong>  if you want to play the game one more time or click <strong>Continue</strong> to learn more interviewing skills.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="incorrect">
                    <p>Uh-oh! Looks like you missed a few reasons or picked the wrong reasons. </p>
                    <p>Imagine if you were interviewing the candidate for the wrong reasons. The impact is significant not just on your performance, but also  the entire organization’s performance and credibility and on the candidate as well.</p>
                    <p>You may wish to <strong>Play Again</strong>, or select <strong>Continue</strong> to reinforce your knowledge on interviewing basics. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="btns"><a class="btn" id="btn_tryagain" style="  background-image: url('images/custom.png');  width: 94px;  height: 42px;  background-repeat: no-repeat;  margin: 0px -50px;"><span style="margin-left:-10px;">Play Again</span></a><a class="btn" id="btn_moveon" style="  background-image: url('images/cnt_btn_new.png');  width: 90px;  height: 42px; background-repeat: no-repeat;  margin: 0px 89px; position: absolute;"><span style="margin-left:-10px;"><span style="margin-left:-14px;">Continue</span></a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
  <div id="canvas">
            <div class="sky">
                <div class="timer"><div class="slot secs" id="time">30</div></div>
                <div class="timer score"><div class="slot secs" id="points">0/5</div></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_1"><a><span>Make Friends</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_2"><a><span>Legal Obligations</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_3"><a><span>Meet Potential Employee</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_4"><a><span>Assess Best Fit</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_5"><a><span>Promote Organization</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_6"><a><span>Gather personal information</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_7"><a><span>Validate Information</span></a><i></i></div>
                <div class="balloon" id="bal_8"><a><span>Judge the candidate</span></a><i></i></div>
            </div>
        </div>        
</div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        parent.next_disable();
        var cur_step = 0; var click_count = 0;
        $(window).ready(function() {
            parent.loadAudioTranscript('module1_2','',true,false);
        });

        var anim_effects = Array(); var score = 0; 
        anim_effects[1]  = Array( 1, 3, 100, 30, 0 );
        anim_effects[2]  = Array( 2, 2, 123, 35, 1 );
        anim_effects[3]  = Array( 3, 1, 376,  5, 1 );
        anim_effects[4]  = Array( 4, 3, 685, 25, 1 );
        anim_effects[5]  = Array( 1, 2, 700,  0, 1 );
        anim_effects[6]  = Array( 4, 1,  24,  17, 0 );
        anim_effects[7]  = Array( 1, 3, 293,  9, 1 );
        anim_effects[8]  = Array( 2, 2, 160,  13, 0 );
       
    var step_handle = Array(); var cur_time = 30; var timer_handle;
        
        $("#btn_start").click(function(){ 
            parent.unloadAudioTranscript();
            $('.resultbg').fadeOut('normal');
            $('#idiv').fadeOut('normal',function() { startPlay(); });
        });
        
        $("#btn_tryagain").click(function(){
            parent.next_disable();
            $('.resultbg').fadeOut('normal');
            $('.balloon').removeClass('visited');
            $('#rdiv').fadeOut('normal',function() {  $('#rdiv').removeClass('correct').removeClass('incorrect'); startPlay(); });
            parent.unloadAudioTranscript();
        });
        
        $("#btn_moveon").click(function(){ 
             parent.gotoPage(3);
             
        });
        
        function startPlay() { 
            cur_time = 30; score=0;
            $('#points').html(score+'/5');
            $('.balloon').removeClass('right').removeClass('wrong');
            $('.balloon').css('top','600px'); 
            $('.balloon').css('display','inline-block'); 
            timer_handle = setInterval('setTime()',1000);
            for(i=1;i<=$('.balloon').length;i++) {                
                $("#bal_"+i).addClass('bal'+anim_effects[i][0]);
                $("#bal_"+i).addClass('wobble'+anim_effects[i][1]); 
                $("#bal_"+i).css('margin-left',anim_effects[i][2]+'px');
                tmr = Math.floor(Math.random() * i) + 1; 
                step_handle[i] = setTimeout("startAnim("+i+")",(anim_effects[i][3]*660));                
            }
        }
        
        $(".balloon").click(function() {
            if($(this).hasClass('visited')){}
            else
            {
            var tmp = $(this).attr('id').split("_"); var itm = tmp[1];
            //$('#bal_'+itm+' A i').show(''); 
            if(anim_effects[itm][4]==1) { 
               $('#bal_'+itm).addClass('right');
               score++;
             } 
            else { 
                $('#bal_'+itm).addClass("wrong"); 
                score--; if(score<0) score = 0;
            }
            updateScore();
            $(this).addClass('visited');
            }
        });
        
        function updateScore() { 
            $('#points').html(score+'/5');
        }
        
        function startAnim(ch) { 
            $("#bal_"+ch).animate({ 
                'top':'-300px',
            }, {
                duration: 9000,
                specialEasing: {
                            width: "linear",
                            height: "linear"
                          },
                complete: function() {  
                }
            });
        }
        
        function btnBurst(itm) {
            //$('#bal_'+itm+' A i').hide(''); 
        }
        
        function setTime(){
            if(cur_time>0) {
                cur_time--;
                if(cur_time>4) $('#time').html(cur_time); else $('#time').html('0'+''+cur_time); 
                if($(".blip").hasClass('hide')) $('.blip').removeClass('hide'); else $('.blip').addClass('hide'); 
            }
            else { clearInterval(timer_handle); closePlay(); }
        }
        
        function closePlay(){ 
            $('.resultdiv h3').html('Score : '+Math.round( ( score / 5 ) * 100) + "% ("+score+"/5)"); 
            cur_step = 1;
            if(score==5) { $('#rdiv').addClass('correct');  parent.loadAudioTranscript('module1_2_correct','',true,true); } 
            else { $("#rdiv").addClass('incorrect');  parent.loadAudioTranscript('module1_2_incorrect','',true,true); }
        }
        function postAudioPlay(){                                    
            if(cur_step == 0) {
                if($('#content').css('visibility')=='hidden') {
                    $('#content').css('display','none');
                    $('#content').css('visibility','visible').fadeIn('normal');
                    $("#canvas").fadeIn('normal');
                    $(".resultbg").fadeIn('normal');
                    $('#idiv').fadeIn('normal');
                }
            }
            else if(cur_step == 1) {
                $('.resultbg').fadeIn('normal');
                $('#rdiv').fadeIn('normal');
            }
            else if(cur_step == 2) {
                alert();
            }
            cur_step = -1;
        }
        
    </script>
</body>
</html>